https://fbinfer.com
https://github.com/facebook/infer

As of 2026-04-23, the latest release is 1.2.0, dated 2026-06-21.
So, install from source:
https://github.com/facebook/infer/blob/main/INSTALL.md#install-infer-from-source

# Preliminaries
sudo apt install -y opam libgmp-dev libsqlite3-dev

# Without setting TMPDIR, it created a directory /tmp/clang-setup.MaQGUp/
# which filled up /tmp/ with 31GB of data and crashed the process.

cd ~/bin/install
git clone https://github.com/facebook/infer.git
# If re-making after a build failure: make clean
./build-infer.sh --only-setup-opam
# `--disable-swift-analyzers` is per https://github.com/facebook/infer/issues/1982
./build-infer.sh -y -- --disable-swift-analyzers
sudo make install
# ...or, alternatively, install Infer into your PATH
# export PATH=`pwd`/infer/bin:$PATH
